Date: 1997-05-05

Title: The Higgs Mechanism in N=2 Superspace

Authors: Norbert Dragon and Sergei Kuzenko (Institut fuer Theoretische Physik,

Universitaet Hannover)Comments: 18 pages, LaTeX, typos are corrected

Journal-ref: Nucl.Phys. B508 (1997) 229-244

We describe the Higgs mechanism for general N=2 super Yang-Mills theories ina manifestly supersymmetric form based on the harmonic superspace.